name: Besieged
Lore: 'Stormtroopers blasted through the main airlock of the Tantive IV. The Rebel soldiers'' attempt to defend the intrusion was no match for the Empire''s superior firepower.',
Text: 'Deploy on a captured starship. Your characters present with captured starship may battle opponent''s characters aboard it (as if present together at a site). Effect canceled if starship escapes or is stolen.',
